    new "It's fine, you can say it."

    old "Northwood."
    new "Northwood."

    old "Varga's house. Newly raised into nobility, his family did not hold much prestige."
    new "Varga's house. Newly raised into nobility, his family did not hold much prestige."

    old "But even a noble of low renown, was still a noble."
    new "But even a noble of low renown, was still a noble."

    old "As I said. Small houses, each with their petty grievances."
    new "As I said. Small houses, each with their petty grievances."

    old "Sarah looked at Marion, impressed with the speed with which he deduced these facts."
    new "Sarah looked at Marion, impressed with the speed with which he deduced these facts."

    old "I didn't know they had complaints..."
    new "I didn't know they had complaints..."

