    new "Yes. We suffered the invasion from the Tribes, and we were victorious only by the luck of the Gods."

    old "But we won in so far as that we are not all in chains."
    new "But we won in so far as that we are not all in chains."

    old "The Eastern provinces...well, the first reports we're getting are quite dire."
    new "The Eastern provinces...well, the first reports we're getting are quite dire."

    old "But we drove them back."
    new "But we drove them back."

    old "Yes, but all the small villages between the borders and the Capital were not so lucky."
    new "Yes, but all the small villages between the borders and the Capital were not so lucky."

    old "They razed them, enslaved the people."
    new "They razed them, enslaved the people."

