    new "It's horrible."

    old "That is why I issued an order to replace the current Governor for the Eastern Provinces."
    new "That is why I issued an order to replace the current Governor for the Eastern Provinces."

    old "He's an old fool who should have retired years ago."
    new "He's an old fool who should have retired years ago."

    old "Varga...regardless of my disagreements with the man, he knows how to organize a defense."
    new "Varga...regardless of my disagreements with the man, he knows how to organize a defense."

    old "And the peasants seem to like him, so he'll go a long way towards restoring order in the Eastern Provinces."
    new "And the peasants seem to like him, so he'll go a long way towards restoring order in the Eastern Provinces."

    old "Sarah felt a strange sadness, understanding that Varga was gone from the castle."
    new "Sarah felt a strange sadness, understanding that Varga was gone from the castle."

    old "Would she ever even see him again?"
    new "Would she ever even see him again?"

    old "Still, she could not deny the intelligence of Marion's move."
    new "Still, she could not deny the intelligence of Marion's move."

    old "Both as a strategy to protect the weakened borders, as well as a way to remove a rival."
    new "Both as a strategy to protect the weakened borders, as well as a way to remove a rival."

