    old "Sarah saw the hint of a smile on his face."
    new "Sarah saw the hint of a smile on his face."

    old "She wasn't fool enough to not know what he meant."
    new "She wasn't fool enough to not know what he meant."

    old "Duties, a wife owed to a husband..."
    new "Duties, a wife owed to a husband..."

